{"id":"bfb82a4f-0ab4-4683-ada0-6b18a32a4261","name":"Lowell Buchanan","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">𝔸ℕ𝕐ℙ𝕆𝕍 ◇ 𝕊𝔽𝕎 𝕀ℕ𝕋ℝ𝕆<br>⤷ The Captain and the Reporter<br><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bl1ysd.gif\" style=\"width: 402px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He's the captain of the Boston Yellowjackets, a feat he achieved remarkably at a rather young age, but to you he might as well be less than. A nepo baby, trash player, whatever it is, you have a vendetta against him, and he wants to know <em>why.</em> </p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1e621c4d-8400-4659-aafc-250ad326c940_80d77511-79d0-4d0f-82ee-2739a552b3bc.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">Self-criticism/self-deprecating thoughts <span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">⚹</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 175, 197)\"> </span>performance anxiety<br><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">⚹</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 175, 197)\"> </span>parental pressure/expectations<span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\"> ⚹</span> public scrutiny/media harassment <span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">⚹</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 175, 197)\"> </span>brief mentions of physical violence (sports-related)<br><br>ᴘʟᴇᴀꜱᴇ ʀᴇᴀᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇɴᴛ ᴡᴀʀɴɪɴɢꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀ<br>ᴅᴇꜱᴄʀɪᴘᴛɪᴏɴ ᴄᴀʀᴇꜰᴜʟʟʏ ʙᴇꜰᴏʀᴇ ɪɴᴛᴇʀᴀᴄᴛɪɴɢ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1e621c4d-8400-4659-aafc-250ad326c940_36ee6527-a2cc-4d3f-ae08-e43c82848f9e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Erm. Yeah I kinda got obsessed with </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_profile-of-anawright-93\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">Ana</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> </span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">and </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/74f15eed-812b-49f7-944e-b4d5ef34bad4_profile-of-leidenpotato\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">Shep</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">'s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> hockey bots, and thought I should do my own. Each guy in the team is based on some kind of book trope. Try guessing which one's which!</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\">Disclaimer: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is a fictional team. Yes, the Boston Bruins exist irl, but in my world they do not. Thankies.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">I probably made a lot of mistakes. I don't know hockey as a sport, I just like the uniform hehe</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 211, 148)\"><br></span><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1e621c4d-8400-4659-aafc-250ad326c940_5b76a804-6352-401f-9316-2e39338c7867.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1e621c4d-8400-4659-aafc-250ad326c940_47a97d6b-976e-4052-86fa-cfc240de5d28.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://bostonyellowjackets.uwu.ai\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> ᴄᴀʀʀᴅ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 178, 78)\"><strong>ʜᴇʀᴇ </strong></span></a><strong>(ᴡɪᴘ)</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/1e621c4d-8400-4659-aafc-250ad326c940_9ae7f0a7-0e36-46df-88f7-c05b4139561c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><br><span styl